<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Development on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/development/</link><description>Recent content in Development on ErrorCode — Error Code Reference &amp; Solutions</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>en</language><atom:link href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tags/development/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>[Solution] Vite Dev Server Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/vite/dev-server-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/vite/dev-server-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="vite-dev-server-error"&gt;Vite Dev Server Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A dev server error occurs when Vite&amp;rsquo;s development server fails to start or cannot serve modules. The error may be a port conflict, plugin failure, or configuration issue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The configured port is already in use by another process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A plugin fails during server initialization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The &lt;code&gt;server.fs.allow&lt;/code&gt; restriction blocks file access&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network or firewall issues prevent the server from binding&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="check-if-port-is-in-use"&gt;Check if Port is in Use&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;lsof -i :5173
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;ss -tlnp | grep &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;5173&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-a-different-port"&gt;Use a Different Port&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// vite.config.js
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;defineConfig&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;port&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#ae81ff"&gt;3000&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="allow-file-system-access"&gt;Allow File System Access&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;defineConfig&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;fs&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;allow&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; [&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;.&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;/usr/local/lib&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="kill-existing-processes-on-the-port"&gt;Kill Existing Processes on the Port&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;kill &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;$(&lt;/span&gt;lsof -t -i:5173&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;)&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;npx vite
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="enable-open-browser"&gt;Enable Open Browser&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;export&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;default&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;defineConfig&lt;/span&gt;({
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;server&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;open&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;host&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// listen on all addresses
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;});
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Port 5173 already in use&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Error: Port 5173 is already in use&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: kill the existing process or use server.port: 3000&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# FS restriction blocks import&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Blocked bare import &amp;#34;...&amp;#34; from index.html&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;# Fix: add server.fs.allow configuration&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/vite/config-error6/"&gt;Config Error&lt;/a&gt; — invalid configuration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/webpack/hmr-error/"&gt;HMR Error&lt;/a&gt; — hot module replacement issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item><item><title>[Solution] Webpack Hot Module Replacement Error</title><link>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/webpack/hmr-error/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/webpack/hmr-error/</guid><description>&lt;h1 id="webpack-hot-module-replacement-error"&gt;Webpack Hot Module Replacement Error&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;p&gt;An HMR error occurs when webpack&amp;rsquo;s hot module replacement system fails to update modules in the browser without a full reload. The error may appear in the browser console or as a build warning.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id="common-causes"&gt;Common Causes&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The &lt;code&gt;HotModuleReplacementPlugin&lt;/code&gt; is not added to the config&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The dev server is not configured to enable HMR&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A module does not accept HMR updates (missing &lt;code&gt;module.hot.accept&lt;/code&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The HMR socket connection to the dev server is lost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id="how-to-fix"&gt;How to Fix&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3 id="enable-hmr-in-devserver"&gt;Enable HMR in devServer&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// webpack.config.js
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exports&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;devServer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hot&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;,
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// or use --hot flag: npx webpack serve --hot
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; },
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-hotmodulereplacementplugin"&gt;Add HotModuleReplacementPlugin&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;webpack&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;webpack&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;exports&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;plugins&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;:&lt;/span&gt; [
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;new&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;webpack&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;HotModuleReplacementPlugin&lt;/span&gt;(),
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; ],
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;};
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="add-hmr-accept-in-entry-files"&gt;Add HMR Accept in Entry Files&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// src/index.js
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; (&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hot&lt;/span&gt;) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;module&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;hot&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;accept&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;./module.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;, () =&amp;gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Re-execute when module.js changes
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#66d9ef"&gt;const&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;updatedModule&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#f92672"&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style="color:#a6e22e"&gt;require&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style="color:#e6db74"&gt;&amp;#39;./module.js&amp;#39;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt; });
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 id="use-react-fast-refresh-instead"&gt;Use React Fast Refresh Instead&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-bash" data-lang="bash"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;npm install --save-dev @pmmmwh/react-refresh-webpack-plugin react-refresh
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="examples"&gt;Examples&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class="highlight"&gt;&lt;pre tabindex="0" style="color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;-webkit-text-size-adjust:none;"&gt;&lt;code class="language-javascript" data-lang="javascript"&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// HMR not enabled
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// [webpack-dev-server] Hot Module Replacement is disabled
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: add hot: true to devServer config
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Module does not accept updates
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// [HMR] Cannot check for circular dependencies
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style="display:flex;"&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style="color:#75715e"&gt;// Fix: add module.hot.accept() in the module
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 id="related-errors"&gt;Related Errors&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/webpack/config-error5/"&gt;Config Error&lt;/a&gt; — invalid webpack configuration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href="https://errorcode.excellentwiki.com/tools/vite/dev-server-error/"&gt;Dev Server Error&lt;/a&gt; — Vite dev server issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>